      <div class="msgContentFrame">I was thinking of reassigning all my stats for tanking and leveling gladiator instead of lancer cos theres not enough good tanks around. But i was thinking of dividing my stats between VIT (obviously) and MND for the healing potency (id be leveling CON to make sure i have good heals) Thats the most important factors of a tank, lots of hp and the ability to stay alive and hold aggro (which the heals will do) Str is kinda pointless cos u dont need 2 do damage thats not your role and dex is also not really required except for the accuracy to generate TP.  <br /> <br />Can someone please confirm, or explain why its not the case that i should be focusing on VIT and MND.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4454266" title="http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4454266" rel="external nofollow">http://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4454266</a> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1812910.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
